# Quality & WOW — Règles impératives

# UI MUST follow Mobile Playbook
- Treat the product as a MOBILE APP. Prefer native-app patterns.
- Never use table/grid/spreadsheet layouts for tournament/match data.
- Tournament "tables" MUST be rendered as MATCH CARDS (sports/game match card).
- Score must be the most prominent element on match cards.
- No generic labels like "TABLE". Use "Table X" and card suit cues (♠♥♦♣).
- Keep UI consistent across sibling pages (auth/login, auth/signup, auth/forgot).
- Implement empty/loading/error states using Shadcn Skeleton/Alert/Toast patterns.